ting the same tab in the Options menu to reset the displayed options.\n\t\u2022 Added a \"Revert\" button to allow you to undo changes you've made in the settings menu.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing a random floating box sometimes to appear in the settings menu.", "created_date": 1728105167, "id": "8882155375150329", "version": "0.2.1.1", "version_code": 78, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5752649148100983", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8984001048299094"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "794265068422855"}]}, "change_log": "1) New option to hide built in songs and playlists!\n\t\u2022 Built in songs and playlists can now be individually hidden. They can be unhidden in the settings menu under Player Settings.\n\n2) Bug Fixes:\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing songs to resume from paused immediately despite displaying countdown sometimes.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing easy and normal difficulty on jabs only to force every obstacle to include duplicate targets with every obstacle sometimes.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug deleting a playlist to sometimes throw an error.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing the home page to not update after songs are downloaded.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing workouts with missing songs to be playable resulting in errors being thrown.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing notifications to stack and not pull the next notification correctly resulting in unexpected function.\n\t\u2022 Fixed bug causing playlists to sometimes not delete after confirming to delete them.", "created_date": 1727584542, "id": "8826134990752368", "version": "0.2.1", "version_cod